Receipts are required for all expenses above the local threshold, and reimbursement requests should also be submitted within 30 days.\\n\\n4. **Submission Process**: To submit an expense report, employees should:\\n   - Create a new expense report in the expense tool.\\n   - Mark the payment method as \\\"Personal / Out-of-Pocket\\\" if applicable.\\n   - Attach receipts and provide clear descriptions.\\n   - Select the correct cost center and category.\\n   - Submit the report for manager approval.\\n\\n5. **Policy Exceptions**: Exceptions to the policy may be made for valid business reasons.
